"<b>Ilford SPX 400</b>:<p>Simulate the Ilford SPX infrared film at 400 ISO.</"
"p>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ilford SPX 400</b>:<p>Ilford SPX infravörös film szimulálása ISO 400 "
"beállítással.</p>"

#: core/libs/dimg/filters/bw/bwsepiasettings.cpp:205
