#: core/utilities/fuzzysearch/fuzzysearchview_similar.cpp:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>Drag & drop an image here<br>to perform similar<br>items search.</"
"p><p>You can also use the context menu<br>when browsing through<br>your "
